An 18-year-old Igbo girl living with her parent in the Agiliti area of Mile 12, Lagos, died from starvation and beating by her parent with were angry with her.
Amaka Nweke \s parent were angry because their daughter was in love with a Yoruba man, Ibrahim Lawal, and even had a baby for him.
The baby is named Zaheed.
But Mr. and Mrs. Nweke have denied this.
According to them in a report by the Telegraph, it is impossible for a father to subject her daughter to such.
Amaka and Lawal fell in love when they were in secondary school, and the love ended in a love childZaheed.

			
